The new "Mommy's Charm" -collection was based on the idea of lucky pearls. They say that if you give pearls as a gift to a child, they will guarantee a long life. 

"Mommy's Charm" -collection will have unique composition of few personal charms which are always precious metals and quite natural looking pearls with different shapes and colors. 

The Mommy's Charm "Disc" is unique composition with the peacock shaded freshwater pearl, silver puffy drop, filigree shaped round disc-pedant and small heart pedant. There is also a little bit of sparkle in the small silver roundel with Swarovski crystals. Delicate ball-chain is 90 cm long.

name: Jungle Deluxe "Natural" - leather bracelet with pearls
description:
New F/W 13-14 collection will be here soon!

Romantic but in the same time rough. The new Jungle Deluxe collection was something I dreamed about. 

This bracelet has large lusterious fresh water pearls, wire wrapped and connected with soft leather. All metal parts are sterling silver and they might oxidized in time. 

Please notice that you'll get one bracelet, similar as shown in last picture, fits perfectly different sized wrists because of extension chain.
